<title>反转页面颜色</title>


 <p>To swap black for white, white for black, and so on, click the
 <gui>View options</gui> button in the top-right corner and select
 <gui>Inverted Colors</gui>.</p>


<note style="tip">
 <p>这样做可使文本阅读起来更容易，特别是在某些视觉减弱的条件下。</p>
</note>
